Main article: LuigiLuigi (ルイージ, Ruīji?) is a video game character created by Nintendo game designer Shigeru Miyamoto.
In most games of the main series, Luigi is playable, occasionally as a secret revealed in-game or an unlockable character.
In Super Smash Bros. Brawl, Waluigi is one of the characters who can be summoned using the Assist Trophy item and as an alternate costume for Luigi(However, this is only Luigi in Waluigi's palette).
